# Coriolis Wind Node & Base Station BOM

This Bill of Materials (BOM) contains the parts required to assemble **one Coriolis board system**.

If you are building multiple wind nodes or base stations, multiply the quantities below by the number of units you intend to build.

> **Important:** Purchase a microUSB cable that supports **data transmission**. Charging-only cables will not work for programming or communication.

---

# Printed Parts

**Recommended Print Settings:**
- Material: ASA or PETG
- Infill: 20%
- Walls: 4
- Top/Bottom Layers: 4
- Recommended Protection: Apply Krylon UV-resistant clear coating for improved outdoor durability

| Quantity | Part |
|----------|------|
| 1x | Main Enclosure |
| 1x | Screw-on Antenna |
| 1x | TPU Lid Gasket |
| 3x | Pushbuttons |
| 4x | PCB Mounting Straps |

---

