# Electronics (Wind Node & Base Station)

| Quantity | Part | Notes |
|----------|------|-------|
| 1x | Coriolis Daughterboard | Fully assembled |
| 1x | LilyGO T-Beam V1.2 | 915 MHz version for U.S. users |
| 1x | OLED Display | Non-soldered version of T-Beam recommended |
| 1x | 18650 Lithium-Ion Battery | Flat-top cell required |
| 1x | BMP180 Temperature/Barometric Pressure Sensor | Optional |

> **Weather Protection Recommendation:**  
